					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One of the big points made by Miau=morphcat is: make sure to add sparkly bits. Little extra bits of motion (sparks, coins bouncing, &amp;c) all over the place really help the game feel more alive.<br /><br />In his specific applications, he means that it's sometimes worth dancing around the sprite overdraw limit.</div>

