					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Just palette swapping could perhaps be fast enough? And half the toggle rate could perhaps be good enough, if the hue and luminosity gap isn't too wide. Ideally, you'd swap between neighboring colours. EDIT: or between a colour and a gray roughly of the same luminosity to achieve a few washed out colours. A dynamic range in colour saturation is not something you readily see on the nes.</div>

					
